sequenceDiagram
    participant I as InfoBlox (The Wire)
    participant G as GitHub Actions (Atlas)
    participant S as ServiceNow (The Business)
    participant T as MS Teams (SecOps)

    I->>G: Extract Subnet/IP Data
    G->>G: Transform to CMDB Schema
    G->>S: Upsert CIs (Correlation ID)
    S-->>G: Ack: Success/Update
    G->>T: Post Adaptive Card Summary
